                            <comment id="17466597" author="rensgroothuijsen" created="Wed, 29 Dec 2021 21:18:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It does appear the bulk loader doesn&apos;t make use of the port parameter, though as a workaround you can specify &quot;-d &amp;lt;host&amp;gt;:&amp;lt;port&amp;gt;&quot; instead of &quot;-d &amp;lt;host&amp;gt;&quot; as the address, and it will work as expected.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17507729" author="smiklosovic" created="Wed, 16 Mar 2022 16:59:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=e.dimitrova&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;e.dimitrova&quot;&gt;e.dimitrova&lt;/a&gt; do you think this is something to fix?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17507783" author="brandon.williams" created="Wed, 16 Mar 2022 18:03:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It seems to be a legitimate bug and was triaged as such, do you disagree?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17507788" author="smiklosovic" created="Wed, 16 Mar 2022 18:12:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;the related PR is just changing some docs (1) and there is a workaround so I was confused. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(1) &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/pull/1374/files&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/pull/1374/files&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17508254" author="smiklosovic" created="Thu, 17 Mar 2022 15:44:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The problem is that native port is resolved after hosts are and default port is 9042 so there is no chance that hosts resoluion would use native port from the  configuration because its parsing is done after hosts are configured. Simple movement of native port resolution solves the issue.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/pull/1507&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/pull/1507&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17508868" author="brandon.williams" created="Fri, 18 Mar 2022 15:21:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1.  It&apos;s a little sad that LoaderOptionsTest couldn&apos;t catch this.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17509269" author="smiklosovic" created="Sat, 19 Mar 2022 13:34:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;ci failed on one test, fixing it ....&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17509514" author="smiklosovic" created="Sun, 20 Mar 2022 20:16:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;4.0 &lt;a href=&quot;https://ci-cassandra.apache.org/view/patches/job/Cassandra-devbranch/1524&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://ci-cassandra.apache.org/view/patches/job/Cassandra-devbranch/1524&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;trunk: &lt;a href=&quot;https://ci-cassandra.apache.org/view/patches/job/Cassandra-devbranch/1525&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://ci-cassandra.apache.org/view/patches/job/Cassandra-devbranch/1525&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
